p6VsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2p6VsT.jpg&h=212cf672&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b88f234c13f605645b6f061f28730bcda661ba2c","tid":2420774,"uid":227521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"中華*"},{"pid":"990f88d417853112b88745464439b53141cc09f3","tid":2420774,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"共產黨前嘅支那咪又係咁<br />\n好過而家 <br />\n但都係垃圾<br />\n嗰種奴性根深蒂固<br />\n對權力嘅絕對崇拜<br />\n一眾文人 思想家對支那人嘅批判唔係共產黨後嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我係香港人<br />\n唔係華人 漢人 中國人<br />\n我除左祖輩喺中國生活過之外<br />\n我同中國毫無關係<br />\n我只係陰差陽錯喺無經我同意下成為左中國籍"},{"pid":"c92c284d604670575931a7835581a667b18e854a","tid":2420774,"uid":360907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:18:01.000Z","msg":"先唔討論黨做得好唔好<br />\n中國人民啲閪性格同行為已經夠討人厭<br />\n<br />\n所以呢世都唔會認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e6f36b394ca3acc3e44b925b7fa5617da5db4b","tid":2420774,"uid":263349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"根本唔係 <br />\n<br />\n認乜嘢？"},{"pid":"5c2c02be81c41a9e1e9336f53852f7872c17a7c1","tid":2420774,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"呃負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940fd6aeeb154e0287378681a23cadead7da8f01","tid":2420774,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">起底保平安</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0e5d795640d987684256ebd33ccfe72a1e26b71a","tid":2420774,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"睇到啲留言都安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999884fa162b2984ebcfeda2bba46713eb47b075","tid":2420774,"uid":364767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"rep